race.comment: BANDIT CHLOE (8) was a last-start winner from the rails at The Meadows over 525m (30.26), scoring by 1.5 lengths. Should be in this for a long way. RHYTHMIC ENERGY (2) was below best last time at The Meadows (30.64) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 7 length seventh. Has already won two times from this draw. Suited here and expected to run well. BLINKED (7) is another with top-three prospects. Something for the Multiples: PAW MAUD (1)

runners.name: Bandit Chloe
runners.owners: Robert Royce Racing - Mgr L Sutherland
